messages.messageBody:
I know many of you are thinking of the Jenners, even if you don't know
them personally and I wanted to pass this new information along...
There has been an email list set up specifically for organizing help
over the next two years as Hannah is treated with chemo.

If you'd like to join, it's open to everyone (but Diana and family)
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/DianaHelp/

So if it's in your heart to help, feel free to join. There is talk of
setting up a webpage of items for sale that will be donated to them.
So people like me that are short on money right now, can make things
and help. Anyway, come on over if you'd like to get involved or keep
up on the plans.:)

Thanks everyone,

Ren
learninginfreedom.com
